In [40]:
train_folder = "C:\\Users\\pdhru\\Downloads\\data\\data\\train"
class_folders = os.listdir("C:\\Users\\pdhru\\Downloads\\data\\data\\train")
sample_images = []
for class_folder in class_folders:
    class_path = os.path.join(train_folder, class_folder)
    sample_image_path = os.path.join(class_path, os.listdir(class_path)[0])
    sample_images.append(load_img(sample_image_path, target_size=(224, 224)))

plt.figure(figsize=(18, 18))
for i, image in enumerate(sample_images):
    ax= plt.subplot(3,6,i *2 +1)
    plt.imshow(image)
    plt.title(" original")
    plt.axis("off")

    image_array = img_to_array(image)
    image_array = image_array.reshape((1,) + image_array.shape)

    augmented_images = train_aug.flow(image_array, batch_size=1)
    for j in range(5):
        augmented_image = next(augmented_images)[0]
        ax = plt.subplot(3,6,i * 2 +j + 2)
        plt.imshow(augmented_image)
        plt.title(" augmented")
        plt.axis("off")
    plt.tight_layout()
    plt.show()

In [50]:
# Class prediction
Y_pred = model.predict(validatation_dataset_gen)
y_pred = np.argmax(Y_pred, axis=1)  

# Calculateing confusion matrix 
confusion = tf.math.confusion_matrix(validatation_dataset_gen.classes, y_pred)
print('Confusion Matrix:')
print(confusion)

# Calculating precision 
true_positives = tf.linalg.diag_part(confusion)
false_positives = tf.reduce_sum(confusion, axis=0) - true_positives
false_negatives = tf.reduce_sum(confusion, axis=1) - true_positives

precision = true_positives / (true_positives + false_positives)
recall = true_positives / (true_positives + false_negatives)

# Calculate F1-score 
f1_score = 2 * (precision * recall) / (precision + recall)
print('Precision:', precision.numpy())
print('Recall:', recall.numpy())
print('F1-Score:', f1_score.numpy())
